        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Now I'm really sailing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "It's great!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "He was very enthusiastic, and Tom himself was not a little pleased at his own success, for certainly the airship had looked to be a very dubious proposition at first.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Bless my gaiters!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "But we are doing pretty well,\" remarked mr Damon, looking down on the field where mr Fenwick's friends and the machinists were gathered, cheering and waving their hands.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"We'll do better,\" declared Tom.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "It needed some adjustments, which he made.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "It was about two hundred feet high, but soon after the gas began to enter the bag it rose until it was nearly five thousand feet high.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "This satisfied Tom that the airship could do better than he expected, and he decided to return nearer earth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "In going down, he put the craft through a number of evolutions designed to test her ability to answer the rudders promptly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"No, I think we've done enough for the first day,\" said Tom, \"But I'd like you to handle her now, mr Fenwick.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Yes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "I guess I can make a landing all right,\" assented the inventor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"I'm better at coming down than going up.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "He did make a good descent, and received the congratulation of his friends as he stepped from the airship.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Tom was also given much praise for his success in making the craft go at all, for mr Fenwick and his acquaintances had about given up hope that she ever would rise.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "This promise was kept two days later.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "They were busy days for Tom, mr Fenwick and the latter's assistants.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Tom sent a short note to his father telling of the proposed long flight, and intimated that he might make a call in Shopton if all went well.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "He also sent a wire to Miss Nestor, hinting that she might have some apple turnovers ready for him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "But Tom never called for that particular pastry, though it was gotten ready for him when the girl received his message.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "All was in readiness for the long flight, and a preliminary test had demonstrated that the WHIZZER had been wonderfully improved by the changes Tom made.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "The young inventor looked over the supply of food mr Fenwick had placed aboard, glanced at the other stores, and asked:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"How long do you expect to be gone, mr Fenwick?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"That's quite a while,\" responded Tom.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"We may be glad to return in two days, or less.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "But I think we're all ready to start.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"I guess we three will make up the party this time, though if our trip is a successful one I'll be overwhelmed with requests for rides, I suppose.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "As before, a little crowd gathered to see the start.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "The day was warm, but there was a slight haziness which Tom did not like.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "He hoped, though, that it would pass over before they had gone far.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Do you wish to head for any particular spot, mr Fenwick?\" asked Tom, as they were entering the cabin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "I have a friend who has a summer cottage there, and he was always laughing at my airship.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "An auspicious start was made, the WHIZZER taking the air after a short flight across the ground, and then, with the lifting gas aiding in pulling the craft upward, the airship started to sail high over the city of Philadelphia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "So swiftly did it rise that the cheers of the little crowd of mr Fenwick's friends were scarcely heard.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Now you steer,\" the lad invited mr Fenwick.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Take her straight across the Delaware River, and over camden new jersey, and then head south, for Cape May.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "We ought to make it in an hour, for we are getting up good speed.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Leaving the owner in charge of his craft, to that gentleman's no small delight, Tom and mr Damon began an inspection of the electrical and other machinery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Several times the young investor looked out of the windows with which the cabin was fitted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "mr Damon noticed this.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Bless my shoe laces, Tom,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"What's the matter?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"I don't like the looks of the weather,\" was the answer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"I think we're in for a storm.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Then let's put back.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"No, it would be too bad to disappoint mr Fenwick, now that we have made such a good start.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"But if there's danger-\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "However, it was in their favor, aiding them to make faster time.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "The speed of the WHIZZER was now about forty miles an hour, not fast for an air craft, but sufficiently speedy in trying out a new machine.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Tom looked at the barograph, and noted that they had attained an altitude of seven thousand five hundred feet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"That's better than millionaire Daxtel's distance of seven thousand one hundred and five feet,\" remarked the lad, with a smile, \"and it breaks Jackson's climb of seven thousand three hundred and three feet, which is pretty good for your machine, mr Fenwick.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Do you really think so?\" asked the pleased inventor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Yes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "And we'll do better than that in time, but it's best to go slow at first, until we see how she is standing the strain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "This is high and fast enough for the present.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Now to drop down and visit my friend,\" said mr Fenwick, with a smile.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Won't he be surprised!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"I don't think we'd better do it,\" said Tom.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Why not?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Well, the wind is getting stronger every minute and it will be against us on the way back.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "If we descend, and try to make another ascension we may fail.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000043_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000043_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "We're up in the air now, and it may be easy to turn around and go back.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000043_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000043_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Then, again, it may not, but it certainly will be easier to shift around up here than down on the ground.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000043_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000043_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "So I'd rather not descend-that is, not entirely to the ground.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Well, just as you say, though I wanted my friend to know I could build a successful airship.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Oh, we can get around that.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"That's a good idea,\" assented mr Fenwick.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Tom sent the WHIZZER down until the hotels and cottages could be made out quite plainly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "After looking with a pair of opera glasses, mr Fenwick picked out the residence of his friend, and Tom prepared to circle about the roof.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "By this time the presence of the airship had become known to hundreds, and crowds were eagerly watching it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000049_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000049_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"I'll drop him a message!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000050_000001",
