        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "I thought you said my airship would never go!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "Whether the gentleman understood what mr Fenwick shouted at him is doubtful, but he saw the inventor waving his hand, and he saw the falling cylinder, and a look of astonishment spread over his face, as he ran to pick up the message.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Bless my storage battery!\" cried mr Damon.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"A much better one than we'll have going back,\" observed Tom, in a low voice.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7608/115034/7608_115034_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7608",
        "content": "\"Why; what's the matter?\" asked the eccentric man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7608_115034_000058_000000",
